od A</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2016-01-01</gtr:date></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/D412E287-61B0-4AC9-BF3F-D4ACCA496241"><gtr:id>D412E287-61B0-4AC9-BF3F-D4ACCA496241</gtr:id><gtr:title>Transverse, propagating velocity perturbations in solar coronal loops</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Plasma Physics and Controlled Fusion</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/406a590b9d5e9e187f5baf7c775e57e1"><gtr:id>406a590b9d5e9e187f5baf7c775e57e1</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>De Moortel I.</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2016-01-01</gtr:date></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/D03D7721-40A8-44CE-A161-6765F94B77EF"><gtr:id>D03D7721-40A8-44CE-A161-6765F94B77EF</gtr:id><gtr:title>Shock heating in numerical simulations of kink-unstable coronal loops</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Philosophical Transactions of the Royal Society of London Series A</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/d8aa38acfebaaf8909183ef83f3789f5"><gtr:id>d8aa38acfebaaf8909183ef83f3789f5</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Bareford M. R.</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2015-01-01</gtr:date></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/B356BC32-0253-4357-9ADE-DAE1D6D3F3AC"><gtr:id>B356BC32-0253-4357-9ADE-DAE1D6D3F3AC</gtr:id><gtr:title>An MHD Avalanche in a Multi-threaded Coronal Loop.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>The Astrophysical Journal</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/0d2df50d9fe6f92154563af2c72e62b2"><gtr:id>0d2df50d9fe6f92154563af2c72e62b2</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Hood A. W.</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2016-01-01</gtr:date></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/EFFBB36E-F6C4-4777-B1D9-D1D98E5DCC57"><g